1
00:00:11,120 --> 00:00:12,000
Take him away.

2
00:00:12,560 --> 00:00:13,240
Go.

3
00:00:21,720 --> 00:00:22,960
Su Cheng absconded to avoid punishment

4
00:00:22,960 --> 00:00:24,320
and was brought to justice.

5
00:00:24,320 --> 00:00:28,240
His Majesty ordered me to take full responsibility for the execution.

6
00:00:28,240 --> 00:00:29,280
Yu,

7
00:00:29,560 --> 00:00:31,200
why must you take his life?

8
00:00:31,200 --> 00:00:32,800
It's not that I want his life.

9
00:00:34,080 --> 00:00:36,120
He never thought of letting us go.

10
00:00:44,640 --> 00:00:46,700
Su Cheng is clearly not the murderer.

11
00:00:46,880 --> 00:00:48,520
Why did he confess?

12
00:00:52,960 --> 00:00:54,360
I can't sit back and watch

13
00:00:54,840 --> 00:00:56,400
Mo Yu being used.

14
00:00:57,200 --> 00:00:59,200
But he will be executed tomorrow.

15
00:01:00,560 --> 00:01:02,240
If I die,

16
00:01:02,240 --> 00:01:04,300
bury me under the yellow flower tree.

17
00:02:08,199 --> 00:02:09,400
Why is it you?

18
00:02:10,840 --> 00:02:12,040
Why is it you?

19
00:02:13,000 --> 00:02:14,520
You... you're not dead.

20
00:02:14,800 --> 00:02:16,640
I should be asking you that.

21
00:02:21,280 --> 00:02:23,210
Su Cheng actually didn't kill her,

22
00:02:23,280 --> 00:02:24,940
but imprisoned her in secret.

23
00:02:25,640 --> 00:02:27,440
It seems she knows something.

24
00:02:31,800 --> 00:02:33,560
You've been secretly locked up here.

25
00:02:33,560 --> 00:02:35,160
Looks like you've suffered a lot.

26
00:02:35,160 --> 00:02:36,600
Do you know something?

27
00:02:40,000 --> 00:02:41,280
I do.

28
00:02:44,200 --> 00:02:46,240
Do you want to know the truth?

29
00:02:46,240 --> 00:02:48,000
Kowtow to me three times first,

30
00:02:48,000 --> 00:02:49,240
then kill yourself.

31
00:02:50,320 --> 00:02:53,800
I might consider telling the truth to your corpse.

32
00:02:53,800 --> 00:02:56,120
Someone is using Mo Yu to frame Su Cheng.

33
00:02:56,120 --> 00:02:57,780
He will be executed tomorrow.

34
00:02:58,520 --> 00:03:00,380
Only he has the key to your chains.

35
00:03:00,680 --> 00:03:03,480
You don't want to starve to death in prison, do you?

36
00:03:04,800 --> 00:03:06,240
Are you threatening me?

37
00:03:06,800 --> 00:03:08,800
I won't tell you even if I die.

38
00:03:09,080 --> 00:03:11,600
The more you suffer, the happier I am.

39
00:03:13,400 --> 00:03:15,120
We grew up together.

40
00:03:16,120 --> 00:03:17,850
I have never owed you anything.

41
00:03:18,920 --> 00:03:20,079
What exactly did I do

42
00:03:20,079 --> 00:03:21,520
to make you hate me so much,

43
00:03:21,520 --> 00:03:22,960
trying to kill me again and again?

44
00:03:22,960 --> 00:03:24,280
Because you are a jinx.

45
00:03:25,040 --> 00:03:27,079
Everyone around you will suffer.

46
00:03:27,360 --> 00:03:29,160
Didn't you want to know the truth?

47
00:03:29,160 --> 00:03:30,440
The truth is,

48
00:03:31,840 --> 00:03:33,720
everything that happened to everyone

49
00:03:33,720 --> 00:03:35,160
is because of you.

50
00:03:35,480 --> 00:03:38,210
And you will ignorantly watch the people you love

51
00:03:38,320 --> 00:03:39,780
and those who love you die.

52
00:03:40,680 --> 00:03:42,040
This is your retribution.

53
00:03:42,040 --> 00:03:43,400
You say I'm a jinx

54
00:03:43,720 --> 00:03:45,380
and will have my retribution.

55
00:03:48,200 --> 00:03:49,120
Let me tell you.

56
00:03:51,000 --> 00:03:52,960
I am the legitimate daughter of the Mu family.

57
00:03:52,960 --> 00:03:55,620
You are just an unwanted concubine's daughter.

58
00:03:55,640 --> 00:03:57,500
We're both fleeing for our lives,

59
00:03:57,520 --> 00:03:59,680
but I am a respected princess,

60
00:03:59,680 --> 00:04:02,040
while you are a living dead without even freedom.

61
00:04:02,040 --> 00:04:02,640
Tell me,

62
00:04:02,960 --> 00:04:04,360
where is my retribution?

63
00:04:04,480 --> 00:04:06,640
Mu Jiuyun, you will die a horrible death!

64
00:04:06,640 --> 00:04:08,440
I am your own sister.

65
00:04:08,720 --> 00:04:10,240
You are the culprit.

66
00:04:11,160 --> 00:04:14,840
If you hadn't been so nosy and saved Gu Chengyu ten years ago,

67
00:04:14,840 --> 00:04:16,720
none of this would have happened.

68
00:04:16,720 --> 00:04:18,320
It's all because of you.

69
00:04:25,600 --> 00:04:27,360
I want to ask you about someone.

70
00:04:27,360 --> 00:04:28,200
Who?

71
00:04:29,240 --> 00:04:31,700
The illegitimate son of the former emperor,

72
00:04:32,400 --> 00:04:33,680
Gu Chengyu.

73
00:04:38,560 --> 00:04:41,240
Hiding the illegitimate son of the former emperor

74
00:04:41,240 --> 00:04:43,560
is a crime punishable by the execution of your entire family.

75
00:04:43,560 --> 00:04:45,000
Don't you know that?

76
00:04:45,000 --> 00:04:46,080
My Gu family

77
00:04:46,480 --> 00:04:48,409
has absolute loyalty to the court.

78
00:04:48,720 --> 00:04:51,000
Please show mercy.

79
00:04:51,000 --> 00:04:51,920
Even if I don't know,

80
00:04:51,920 --> 00:04:53,240
others do.

81
00:04:54,040 --> 00:04:55,440
If you want to live,

82
00:04:55,720 --> 00:04:57,440
there is only one way.

83
00:04:57,440 --> 00:04:58,560
What way?

84
00:04:59,720 --> 00:05:01,360
Be obedient and listen to me.

85
00:05:01,720 --> 00:05:03,680
Help me find the Pill Manual.

86
00:05:07,160 --> 00:05:08,890
So the one who ordered my murder

87
00:05:09,240 --> 00:05:11,640
and wanted the Pill Manual was not Su Cheng.

88
00:05:13,200 --> 00:05:14,460
Then who on earth is it?

89
00:05:14,880 --> 00:05:16,640
It was the former Gu Chengyu,

90
00:05:18,160 --> 00:05:20,420
the grandfather of the current Su Cheng.

91
00:05:27,080 --> 00:05:28,480
Su Cheng's grandfather?

92
00:05:29,640 --> 00:05:31,000
Why did he do this?

93
00:05:31,000 --> 00:05:33,000
Because he has another identity.

94
00:05:33,400 --> 00:05:35,960
The enemy general who commands all spies,

95
00:05:36,560 --> 00:05:37,760
Mo Di.

96
00:05:45,080 --> 00:05:46,120
Mo Yu, oh Mo Yu.

97
00:05:47,280 --> 00:05:49,610
You keep saying you want to protect Ah Yun,

98
00:05:50,520 --> 00:05:52,380
but you ended up as an accomplice.

99
00:05:53,360 --> 00:05:55,800
Are you really going to let a man's jealousy

100
00:05:57,040 --> 00:05:58,720
kill an innocent person?

101
00:06:00,480 --> 00:06:03,160
You provoked me into telling the truth

102
00:06:03,160 --> 00:06:05,420
because you want to save Su Cheng, right?

103
00:06:08,520 --> 00:06:10,680
It's very simple to save Su Cheng.

104
00:06:10,680 --> 00:06:13,610
Just expose Mo Di's identity in front of the Emperor.

105
00:06:13,640 --> 00:06:15,320
But to prove

106
00:06:15,320 --> 00:06:17,560
that Mo Di is the mastermind behind all these plots,

107
00:06:17,560 --> 00:06:19,640
you must have evidence.

108
00:06:19,640 --> 00:06:20,800
And this evidence

109
00:06:21,440 --> 00:06:23,160
comes with a price.

110
00:06:23,480 --> 00:06:25,680
What price? Mo Yu's life?

111
00:06:26,120 --> 00:06:28,600
As long as you are willing to tell the Emperor

112
00:06:28,600 --> 00:06:31,000
that Mo Yu is pretending to be the God of War,

113
00:06:31,520 --> 00:06:33,080
Su Cheng can be saved.

114
00:06:34,000 --> 00:06:35,840
To save Su Cheng,

115
00:06:36,120 --> 00:06:37,560
Mo Yu must die.

116
00:06:37,880 --> 00:06:39,240
To protect Mo Yu,

117
00:06:39,680 --> 00:06:40,720
Su Cheng must die.

118
00:06:41,200 --> 00:06:42,680
No matter what you choose,

119
00:06:43,440 --> 00:06:46,170
you will kill the one you love with your own hands.

120
00:06:46,520 --> 00:06:48,080
This is your retribution.

121
00:06:51,600 --> 00:06:53,560
I can't let Su Cheng die in vain.

122
00:06:57,680 --> 00:06:58,680
Pass on the order.

123
00:06:59,200 --> 00:07:02,000
Go to the execution ground immediately to prepare for the execution.

124
00:07:02,000 --> 00:07:02,680
Yes.

125
00:07:04,360 --> 00:07:05,680
Su Cheng will not die.

126
00:07:06,480 --> 00:07:08,480
Mo Yu will certainly not die either.

127
00:07:09,320 --> 00:07:10,200
Indeed,

128
00:07:10,520 --> 00:07:12,450
exposing Mo Di requires evidence.

129
00:07:12,600 --> 00:07:15,260
Mo Yu pretending to be the God of War is evidence.

130
00:07:15,480 --> 00:07:18,140
My pretending to be a princess is also evidence.

131
00:07:18,160 --> 00:07:20,620
But if saving someone must come with a price,

132
00:07:20,880 --> 00:07:22,480
I am willing to be that price.

133
00:07:37,360 --> 00:07:39,220
This medicine can save your life.

134
00:07:40,159 --> 00:07:41,760
Whether you live or die

135
00:07:42,320 --> 00:07:43,680
depends on yourself.

136
00:08:07,600 --> 00:08:08,060
Baorui.

137
00:08:11,440 --> 00:08:12,370
Zhong Xiaqiang.

138
00:08:12,680 --> 00:08:13,200
Pengyin.

139
00:08:13,200 --> 00:08:14,330
Zijian Qiangqipin.

140
00:08:14,600 --> 00:08:15,330
Quan Xuhang.

141
00:08:16,160 --> 00:08:16,890
Quan Yulong.

142
00:08:17,320 --> 00:08:18,180
Licheng Lefei.

143
00:08:18,760 --> 00:08:19,080
Yunlong Yinyu Jiaguangjing.

144
00:08:19,080 --> 00:08:20,740
Yunlong Yinyu Jiaguangjing.

145
00:08:22,960 --> 00:08:23,240
Luo Xiaocong Linxunbo.

146
00:08:23,240 --> 00:08:23,480
Luo Xiaocong Linxunbo.
